    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little heartbroken to be letting this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for her to find a new home where she\u2019ll be just as pampered. This car is essentially a time capsule\u2014it\u2019s been garage-kept, hand-washed every Sunday, and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. You\u2019d be hard-pressed to find a single blemish; she\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy. She drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh feeling inside. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved with every single mile, this is the one. Come by for a chat and see for yourself why I\u2019m so proud of this gem!",
